- [in English] Phila. let's go.

320
00:19:24.375 --> 00:19:25.791
Where are you taking us?

321
00:19:27.833 --> 00:19:30.083
Do you or do you not want to be CEO?

322
00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:35.000
Listen to my message.

323
00:19:47.083 --> 00:19:48.443
[Zinhle] What's all the commotion?

324
00:19:48.500 --> 00:19:49.916
What commotion?

325
00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:53.333
Phila. Bab' Don. Linda.
something about the CEO thing?

326
00:19:54.125 --> 00:19:57.000
Apparently he wants to show them
something before they... [gulps]

327
00:19:57.083 --> 00:20:00.500
Listen. do you want to get a real drink?
I think I can do with a real drink.

328
00:20:00.583 --> 00:20:03.208
I think I left my phone at the office.
I'll be right back.

329
00:20:04.250 --> 00:20:06.458
Ugh. Okay. come see me when you get back.

330
00:20:07.500 --> 00:20:09.180
[in Sotho] Where do
you think you're going?

331
00:20:09.208 --> 00:20:12.408
- [in English] Left my phone at the office.
- [in Sotho] You can get it tomorrow.

332
00:20:12.708 --> 00:20:15.000
[in English] It's getting late.
Go to your cottage.

333
00:20:24.125 --> 00:20:25.291
Shit!

334
00:20:40.458 --> 00:20:43.625
[Zinhle in Sotho] Apparently he's going
to show them something important.

335
00:20:43.708 --> 00:20:46.166
Listen. I'll call you back.

336
00:20:46.250 --> 00:20:47.250
[phone beeps off]

337
00:20:47.916 --> 00:20:49.166
[in English] Damn!

338
00:20:49.250 --> 00:20:50.416
[horn honks]

339
00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:57.166
Come on!

340
00:21:13.916 --> 00:21:14.916
Fuck!

341
00:21:31.500 --> 00:21:33.625
- Kolobe.
- [Kolobe in Zulu]Â Ngcolosi. hello.

342
00:21:33.708 --> 00:21:35.500
- Bab' Kolobe.
- Linda.

343
00:21:35.583 --> 00:21:36.583
Phila.

344
00:21:52.708 --> 00:21:53.708
[Grace] Zinhle?

345
00:21:54.208 --> 00:21:55.333
Hey. hey.

346
00:21:56.833 --> 00:21:57.833
Mam' Grace.

347
00:22:00.250 --> 00:22:01.250
[in Sotho] Oh. wow.

348
00:22:02.666 --> 00:22:06.541
Such beautiful dark skin.

349
00:22:08.625 --> 00:22:10.000
Are you feeling cold?

350
00:22:10.541 --> 00:22:11.666
Are you hungry?

351
00:22:12.250 --> 00:22:14.333
You need a place to stay. right?

352
00:22:14.416 --> 00:22:16.625
[thunder rumbles]

353
00:22:18.625 --> 00:22:21.375
When I tell you not to do something.
I expect you to listen.

354
00:22:23.708 --> 00:22:25.500
[in English] It won't happen again.

355
00:22:25.583 --> 00:22:26.875
It better not.

356
00:22:31.041 --> 00:22:32.083
[Grace clicks tongue]

357
00:22:32.166 --> 00:22:35.833
[in Sotho] Rubbish is still rubbish
even in expensive wigs and clothes.

358
00:22:43.750 --> 00:22:46.166
[Phila in English]
Okay. a furniture factory?

359
00:22:47.333 --> 00:22:48.625
