360
00:22:48.708 --> 00:22:51.000
Peter. you can sit anywhere.

361
00:22:58.125 --> 00:22:59.708
[in Xhosa]Â Kolobe. open up.

362
00:23:03.125 --> 00:23:05.875
[in English] Okay. what is this?

363
00:23:07.208 --> 00:23:08.666
"What is this?"

364
00:23:08.750 --> 00:23:10.750
[in Xhosa]
Didn't you say you want to be CEO?

365
00:23:32.750 --> 00:23:35.875
[in English]Â Baba. are you going
to let us know what's going on?

366
00:23:47.500 --> 00:23:51.333
Welcome to
the other side of Bhengu Beauty.

367
00:23:53.166 --> 00:23:56.583
We manufacture and package
skin-bleaching products.

368
00:23:57.708 --> 00:23:59.166
Distribute within the country.

369
00:23:59.250 --> 00:24:03.208
and in Lesotho.
Namibia. Botswana. Zimbabwe

370
00:24:03.291 --> 00:24:05.750
and soon enough.
to the rest of the continent.

371
00:24:07.041 --> 00:24:08.083
Are you serious?

372
00:24:10.833 --> 00:24:12.166
Are you okay with this?

373
00:24:14.125 --> 00:24:16.541
Why wouldn't I be?
I mean. people buy this stuff.

374
00:24:16.625 --> 00:24:19.208
This stuff is poison. all right.

375
00:24:19.291 --> 00:24:20.958
These are banned substances.

376
00:24:21.041 --> 00:24:23.625
Why would you drag
Bhengu Beauty into this illegal shit?

377
00:24:23.708 --> 00:24:26.083
This "illegal shit" is
what started Bhengu Beauty.

378
00:24:26.166 --> 00:24:28.291
Linda. I'm gonna need you
to back me up here.

379
00:24:32.708 --> 00:24:37.333
Look. Phila. this is
a lucrative service that Dad is providing.

380
00:24:37.416 --> 00:24:38.791
You really believe that?

381
00:24:42.125 --> 00:24:45.541
You know what. I'll find my own way home.
Thank you very much.

382
00:24:45.625 --> 00:24:49.666
Yeah. the home you are boasting about
was built with this illegal shit!

383
00:24:53.833 --> 00:24:54.833
[Phila] Did you know?

384
00:24:54.916 --> 00:24:56.236
[in Sotho] What'd you say to him?

385
00:24:56.291 --> 00:24:59.833
[in English] God! You really expected me
to be okay with something like this?

386
00:24:59.916 --> 00:25:02.875
You bloody idiot!
Can't you swallow your pride for once?

387
00:25:04.208 --> 00:25:05.791
