388
00:25:05.875 --> 00:25:10.000
Ngcolosi. Phila just needs time.
I'll make him do whatever he needs to do.

389
00:25:10.083 --> 00:25:11.523
[in Sotho] Please give him a chance.

390
00:25:11.583 --> 00:25:12.750
[in English] He failed.

391
00:25:13.916 --> 00:25:16.500
I'm announcing Linda
at the Foundation Gala.

392
00:25:17.916 --> 00:25:19.500
Ngcolosi. please listen...

393
00:25:45.708 --> 00:25:46.708
Yo.

394
00:25:47.416 --> 00:25:48.416
Yo.

395
00:25:49.458 --> 00:25:52.583
So. how did he make this decision?

396
00:25:53.250 --> 00:25:54.875
[laughs]

397
00:25:54.958 --> 00:25:57.041
Trust me. you do not want to know.

398
00:25:57.916 --> 00:26:00.125
You two are always
playing into his games. man.

399
00:26:00.208 --> 00:26:01.750
What. you think we have a choice?

400
00:26:02.291 --> 00:26:04.708
We're all caught up in this. Trust me.

401
00:26:04.791 --> 00:26:06.500
Even you work for Bhengu Beauty now.

402
00:26:06.583 --> 00:26:07.750
Dude. that's different.

403
00:26:08.958 --> 00:26:10.625
Actually. I have a great idea.

404
00:26:10.708 --> 00:26:13.583
I'm thinking the three of us.
we go out tonight. you know?

405
00:26:13.666 --> 00:26:14.500
Sorry.

406
00:26:14.583 --> 00:26:17.083
[in Xhosa]
Ndu. may I get a second with Phila?

407
00:26:17.166 --> 00:26:19.000
[in English] Don't worry about it. Stay.

408
00:26:20.875 --> 00:26:21.875
Phila...

409
00:26:23.583 --> 00:26:27.666
Don't worry. I am hurt.
but I'm not gonna stoop that low.

410
00:26:27.750 --> 00:26:29.625
Your secrets are safe with me.

411
00:26:29.708 --> 00:26:30.708
Cool.

412
00:26:33.250 --> 00:26:34.416
Cheers. guys.

413
00:26:37.208 --> 00:26:40.458
Wait. Dude. am I missing something?
What secret is this?

414
00:26:41.041 --> 00:26:42.250
No. nothing.

415
00:26:44.083 --> 00:26:47.166
[in Sotho] Whatever he showed them
was enough to disqualify Phila.

416
00:26:47.250 --> 00:26:49.125
[knocking on door]

417
00:26:49.208 --> 00:26:50.250
I'll call you back.

418
00:27:02.375 --> 00:27:05.875
[Grace in English]
I saw the photos Ndumiso took yesterday.

419
00:27:06.875 --> 00:27:08.083
They're good.

420
00:27:08.791 --> 00:27:09.875
[Zinhle] Thank you.

421
00:27:10.916 --> 00:27:13.833
I want him to take more tonight.

422
00:27:14.458 --> 00:27:17.666
Can't you postpone?
I actually have plans with some friends.

423
00:27:19.541 --> 00:27:20.583
No. you don't.

424
00:27:21.750 --> 00:27:23.416
Ndumiso will pick you up.

425
00:27:36.625 --> 00:27:37.625
[in Sotho] Dude.

426
00:27:38.041 --> 00:27:40.875
Grace wants me to do a photoshoot tonight.

427
00:27:40.958 --> 00:27:42.583
[Bonga] <i>And you can't get out of it?</i>

428
00:27:42.666 --> 00:27:43.666
No.

429
00:27:43.750 --> 00:27:45.458
<i>I will ask Vee.</i>

430
00:27:45.541 --> 00:27:46.541
Okay.

431
00:27:47.666 --> 00:27:49.583
Do it. Thanks.

432
00:28:01.333 --> 00:28:04.083
- [Don in English] Thank you.
- What's this about. Ngcolosi?

433
00:28:04.166 --> 00:28:05.375
MaNdebele.

434
00:28:09.083 --> 00:28:11.500
We're going to have to try
for another baby.

435
00:28:15.791 --> 00:28:18.833
[in Sotho] But after her miscarriage.
I don't think she has the ability...

436
00:28:18.916 --> 00:28:20.116
[in Xhosa]Â Simphiwe will help.

437
00:28:20.166 --> 00:28:21.846
[in English]
I should've called her sooner.

438
00:28:23.833 --> 00:28:27.166
Considering what happened the last time.
I don't think it's possible.

439
00:28:27.250 --> 00:28:29.375
[Don in Xhosa] Nothing is impossible.

440
00:28:30.666 --> 00:28:31.750
[in English] That's all.

441
00:28:38.333 --> 00:28:39.541
[woman in Sotho] Yes.

442
00:28:39.625 --> 00:28:41.875
- [laughs] WhatÂ do you think?
- No.

443
00:28:41.958 --> 00:28:44.333
Don't start. Vee.

444
00:28:44.416 --> 00:28:46.375
- [laughs]
- You're being silly.

445
00:28:48.583 --> 00:28:51.791
Okay. Look. Will you be able to do it?

446
00:28:51.875 --> 00:28:54.375
[in English]
Yeah. I think I definitely I can do this.

447
00:28:54.875 --> 00:28:57.375
[in Sotho] I've heard about
these Emerald parties before.

448
00:28:57.458 --> 00:28:58.291
Whoo!

449
00:28:58.375 --> 00:29:00.000
[in English] They are so exclusive.

450
00:29:00.083 --> 00:29:01.750
[in Sotho] Here. It's the password.

451
00:29:03.750 --> 00:29:04.750
[in English] Cool.

452
00:29:06.833 --> 00:29:10.000
[Ndu] We're going to have to take
a few pictures before it starts to rain.

453
00:29:10.083 --> 00:29:12.000
Yes. just give me some of that.

454
00:29:12.541 --> 00:29:14.041
[camera shutter clicking]

455
00:29:14.125 --> 00:29:19.416
Oh my gosh. Actually. do you think
you could actually pose for me over here?

456
00:29:19.500 --> 00:29:20.500
Okay.

457
00:29:21.083 --> 00:29:23.375
[Ndu] Okay. Come on now. yes.

458
00:29:23.458 --> 00:29:26.250
There we go.
Give me that energy. come on. Come on.

459
00:29:26.333 --> 00:29:28.291
Could you tilt back just a little bit?

460
00:29:28.375 --> 00:29:29.208
Whoa. Not too much.

461
00:29:29.291 --> 00:29:32.666
We don't want the face of Bhengu Beauty
falling over the building. now.

462
00:29:32.750 --> 00:29:34.250
[laughs] Imagine.

463
00:29:34.333 --> 00:29:36.500
I don't have to. It almost happened to me.

464
00:29:36.583 --> 00:29:37.625
How?

465
00:29:37.708 --> 00:29:42.375
[sighs] Let's just say...
shots. bad friends. messy time.

466
00:29:43.125 --> 00:29:44.916
Just glad that's over. [chuckles]

467
00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:46.458
[Zinhle chuckles] Jeez.

468
00:29:46.541 --> 00:29:47.625
[Ndu] Check this out.

469
00:29:48.166 --> 00:29:50.250
[thunder cracks]

470
00:29:50.875 --> 00:29:52.083
We should probably go.

471
00:29:52.166 --> 00:29:54.416
- Okay. just one more. Just one more.
- No.

472
00:29:54.500 --> 00:29:55.916
Please. just one or two more.

473
00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:58.833
Please. Give me that energy
that you gave me. Yes!

474
00:29:58.916 --> 00:30:01.708
- [shutter clicking]
- Yes. that's what I'm talking about.

475
00:30:01.791 --> 00:30:03.625
- [laughs]
- Give me that energy. yes!

476
00:30:04.708 --> 00:30:07.000
[automated voice] <i>Welcome to the planet.</i>

477
00:30:07.083 --> 00:30:10.541
["Asambe" by DJ Mr X playing]

478
00:30:16.500 --> 00:30:18.500
[inaudible]

479
00:30:27.125 --> 00:30:30.541
[song continues]

480
00:30:43.958 --> 00:30:45.958
[people cheering]

481
00:31:13.541 --> 00:31:15.541
[shivering]

482
00:31:16.291 --> 00:31:17.375
Ooh!

483
00:31:18.250 --> 00:31:21.458
If I catch a cold. it's on you.

484
00:31:22.000 --> 00:31:23.625
- It will be worth it.
- [exhales]

485
00:31:24.916 --> 00:31:26.041
Look at this.

486
00:31:27.791 --> 00:31:29.166
Your work is amazing.

487
00:31:29.250 --> 00:31:31.916
- [Ndu] Uh-huh. Look at yourself.
